{
  "stem": "15645.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "On the other side, there are big, big woods.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And if you're lucky, you'd find some partisan Russian soldiers or-- and they told me where to go through the canal in the-- in the-- in the place it's not so deep.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "But still, it was-- it was deep, like, [POINTS] over the-- and I went through.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And I went-- and I come to the woods.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And I lay overnight under a tree.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And in the morning, when I-- when I go up, I was looking where to go.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And I saw a, a, a boy-- a boy [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] looking, looking after, after some cows on the-- on the-- on the-- on the-- on the grass.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "So I went to him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Because one boy, I was not afraid for him.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "I go him.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And I ask him how-- did he see some people up here.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "Oh, yes, he, he saw some people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And he showed me where to go.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And I found some people.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "But he, he, he, he knows I am Jewish.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And, and he know where the Jews who runs away, some.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And he told me where to go in, in the direction.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And I went.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And I went maybe an hour or something.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And I-- and I meet a group-- a group, Jewish--",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They, they were from the-- from the ghetto, from the other places.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't ask from where they are, but it was very [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] bad conditions.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Some are burnt, and black faces, and their hands black.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was a terrible-- a terrible look and terrible situation.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it was very bad conditions.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I have some-- from the peasant, I saved some bread.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I gave some of the bread.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
